thread.title_full: Dyers RV reviewed by William D Clark

author: William D Clark
title: William D Clark
text: There were 2 sinks that looked alike on the same web site. One was $24. and the other was $44. The spec sheet didn't offer a lot of info. Thinking the higher price one may be a little heavier duty I ordered it. It was not. If I had it to do over I would order the cheaper on as they appear to be exactly the same. That said, I am happy with the sink. The ordering and delivery process was efficient and on time.
